      "span_text": "Activation of the molecular target of VAF347, AhR, has been shown to promote in vivo the generation of Tr cells.  To investigate the cellular mechanism through which AhR activation mediates the induction of tolerance, we investigated whether oral VAG539 administration and VAG-DC transfer modify the frequency of CD4 ϩ CD25 ϩ Foxp3 ϩ Tr cells."
